Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:18.85,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Soar up to the sky with your gentle heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:26.84,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k17}{\k28}a{\k21}no{\k0} {\k45}ka{\k38}ze{\k0} {\k20}ni{\k0} {\k26}no{\k46}se{\k95}te{\k0} {\k13}i{\k5}s{\k27}se{\k7}i{\k0} {\k10}{\k0} {\k26}no{\k372}se{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:26.84,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ride on that wind, and spread your wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:41.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to act like a real cat, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, why do we have to go so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:48.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:53.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten fat recently, so I'm taking you on a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:56.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is it an earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:59.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten cooler, so my fur just sticks out more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a grasshopper! A grasshopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:07.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The grasshopper's moving! The grasshopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:09.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I was kind of dozing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:21.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:28.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A tattoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:30.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:33.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natori-san! The break's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:36.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:39.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that Natori Shuuichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:42.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natori Shuuichi? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:45.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, he's the actor who recently became popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:46.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:48.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That was surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought sensei disguised himself for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,First you'll have an argument, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:58.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natori... Shuuichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it tied to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a Youkai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:29.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your bandages are coming apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:30.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to tie them back up for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:36.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a human, so don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:42.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, don't just talk to them without giving it any thought, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:49.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I calling out to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:52.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:53.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:58.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-kun, why do you keep making up all these creepy lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:09.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I at least forget about what happened recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:12.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40\bord1.4}Sign: Gone drinking
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:14.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:32.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:01.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:04.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He saw me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:07.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like he could see that thing just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:11.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right. It was nothing, so you don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:13.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You could see the thing just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:23.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,See them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:27.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:28.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:33.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably the ones called Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:43.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You can't tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:47.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We met once this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:53.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Natori. Natori Shuuichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:56.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I tested you, and it seems you can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And your power seems to be quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:02.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm getting too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:04.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:12.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The same?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:15.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wait, Takashi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:20.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot your lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:21.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:26.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You seem out of it this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:28.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:35.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, the sisters brought the corpse that no one else would take to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:38.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:39.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The same?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:44.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he tested me. Was he teasing me or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:49.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:52.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanuma... Yeah, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:55.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:58.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, how can I be so confused like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:02.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, doesn't that person by the gate look like the actor Natori Shuuichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're right, he kind of does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:16.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Natori Shuuichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:20.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:22.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Even {\i1}I{\i0} watch some TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:27.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, if I had to say, he's the type that I wouldn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Walk further away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:34.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:36.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like standing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:39.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being so fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:42.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to have a talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, could you come with me for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:48.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're really human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:53.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Your aura was kind of weird, so I thought you might have been a Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:59.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to help me with my job?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Your job? Do you mean your TV one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, my side job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:08.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually work as an exorcist too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,An exorcist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting an assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:16.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll learn a lot from it, so how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:20.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the money? Do you want money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:23.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:27.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so quick-tempered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:33.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did that tattoo look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The tattoo moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:42.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:44.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see this too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:48.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This birthmark moves all around my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Birthmark?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:54.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was young, I noticed that I had a birthmark around my ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The next day, I thought it had disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but it had moved to my left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It was pretty creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:04.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,After looking it up, I found out that it was a Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:08.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned a lot while trying to find a way to get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all self-study, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:11.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have any effect on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:15.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, so I just left it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:18.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It actually eats your life-span or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:22.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This person has been fighting alone under all that uneasiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:24.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing to laugh about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:30.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this precocious little brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:37.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:38.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he has anemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you bring some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:40.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, don't act on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:48.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:50.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you to be rude to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the rude one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:57.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't speak so friendly to my prey, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:01.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:04.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that odd creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:08.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, we can't have you bringing in a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:09.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:21.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so funny, no matter how many times I look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:25.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, he's my cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:26.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:36.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanko-sensei isn't actually a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:42.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:45.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a cute follower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:47.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not his follower! I'm his master, you greenhorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:50.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! What are you doing to my master, you fat cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say, frizzy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:52.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:53.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:56.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:01.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:56.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40\bord1.4}Sign: Fat Cat vs Frizzy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:04.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,On my right is Sasago, and on my left is Urihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:06.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Youkai that serve me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:11.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a job from a certain old family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:15.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a "forbidden" cellar that supposedly curses you if you open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:18.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They needed money, so they called for a pawner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:23.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The pawner opened the cellar with the key he kept and went in with the family head to have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:27.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, the pawner would have nightmares every night,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:32.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,be in accidents, and have bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:34.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the doing of a Youkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:37.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what these two say after looking into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:41.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since their ancestors locked away their valuables in order to save up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:46.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,a Youkai began to live in the cellar and deny entrance to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They're always so irrational and such an annoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:58.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say anything unless you know their circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nice kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:05.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on the Youkai's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That attitude is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:12.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So you wear glasses, Natori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:15.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,These are fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:21.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier to see Youkai through glasses or mirrors instead of the naked eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I've seen you smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:38.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this birthmark is useful at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:42.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nice kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:45.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a nice kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:46.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:50.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:55.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be at the pawner's employer's house tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:57.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:00.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say I'd help you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:02.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:04.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:08.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over the Book of Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:10.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something in that thicket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:13.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get away or Natori-san will get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:16.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:20.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you don't need to keep any secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:26.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:36.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already! He's wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:38.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:42.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:47.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot let them hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:50.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you do to exorcise Youkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurting them is going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:56.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You should understand, since Youkai have made you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:14:00.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't approve of this method!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:06.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have that kind of annoying mindset, it'll come right back to bite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:10.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, this is a method I can approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:15.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:22.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I finally met someone who can see the same things,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:25.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,is it too hard to understand each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:29.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We both suffered through the same things too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:35.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I could see the hate he had for Ayakashi when I touched him for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:40.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite what he says, he must've gone through a lot with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:43.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Without anyone believing in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:53.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:57.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:02.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who put this rope on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:06.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You have his smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,His?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:16.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been on my mind, so could you let me fix your bandages?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:18.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You can ignore me when I finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:21.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:26.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, a shaman tied this rope to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:29.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be a mountain guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:34.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was caught, tied to that pole, and ordered to protect this family and cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:37.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were always here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There was someone who opened the cellar recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:47.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't fulfill my duty, this rope will constrict and my head will fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:48.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Her nails...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:51.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to run away once,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but I eventually gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:59.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave up and just sat here alone in a daze...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:03.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,For years and years...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:10.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands are bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a human child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you, he could see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:23.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He tied this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:29.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When the cellar opened, I thought it would've been okay to not fulfill my duty and to have my head fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:35.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But fate is a funny thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:40.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That child has come back to this city as an exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:43.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be happy to be a service to that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:46.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yin and Yang are so troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:50.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even thank him for this single strip of cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:05.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I thought you wouldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:09.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Rip up the paper there and cover up the characters on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:15.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the Youkai you're exorcising today, Natori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:20.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's an enslaved Youkai with a rope around its neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:23.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be exorcised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:29.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natori-san doesn't remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:31.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stop her from coming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:40.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:46.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:58.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Natori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:10.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:13.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything, so stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:16.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop the spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:33.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:45.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:47.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:49.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hand is bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:57.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When I fell, my mom treated me this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom isn't around anymore, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She had a weak body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:10.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The old men say I called forth bad luck because I can see weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:16.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But if so, someone should've just gotten rid of me before that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk a lot, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:23.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a child, I'm Shuuichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:31.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, human children do not have the power to call forth bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:32.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:35.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nice child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:38.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a nice child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:43.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:48.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It was that Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:03.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The curse on her neck has been lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:05.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the chances would be 50/50.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:09.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was a helpless Youkai that couldn't be freed from its curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:12.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to let them go in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:18.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it had gone well, then perhaps the rope would've burned off and it'd be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you saved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry though, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:27.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to get you involved like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:32.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at you, it reminds me of my old self,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and I thought I could teach you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:38.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:43.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:48.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't have someone reckless like you as my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:51.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:52.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not cute at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:55.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? Why did you become so peevish?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:58.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You were such a pure child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:00.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:05.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you call me naive, I can't approve of your methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:07.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:10.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to have the same opinion on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:14.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Understanding others is a difficult thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:16.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,For everyone, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're ever in trouble, you can call me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:23.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be helpful to my friend too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:39.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That Youkai girl is finally free,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:44.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,yet she was given the name Hiiragi and is going to serve Natori.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be her own will, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:48.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's fallen for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:55.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are times when only they themselves know what makes them happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:57.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:01.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
